item.title: I need desprit help please!
item.dc:creator: @Zombiedevice Zombiedevice
item.description:
@Zombiedevice wrote:

Put in the blank spot “ABC1.” Then go in your fire wall and click the “exceptions” tab. Then click “add port.” Type in “ABC1” for the name and your port that your using for the port. Make sure you check “TCP.”
